Package: ggviolinbox
Type: Package
Title: Half violin and boxplot geoms for extended ggplot2 graphics 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Daniil", "Smutin", email = "dvsmutin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The ggviolinbox package extends ggplot2 by providing custom geoms for creating half-violin plots, half-boxplots, and combinations of both. These functions are useful for visualizing distributions and comparisons in a compact and elegant way.
